/-- **Theorem 11.4 constant (Higham [608, 1997], eq (4.13))**: the `36` in the
bound `‚ÄĖ|LŐā||DŐā||LŐāŠĶÄ|‚ÄĖ_M ‚Č§ 36 n ŌĀ‚āô ‚ÄĖA‚ÄĖ_M` comes from
